---

## 0. PURPOSE

The PantheonOS Treasury is the complete economic subsystem of the OS — not money, but cognitive, narrative, ethical, temporal, luck, symbolic, and alignment capital.

This is the economic engine of the entire Pantheon. It defines how value is created, accumulates, compounds, flows, is preserved, and is transmitted across models and generations.

**This is the economic heart of PantheonOS.**

