## 5. THE COMPOUND CLARITY ENGINE

(Pantheon’s version of compounding interest)

PantheonOS compounds not money, but clarity.

$$C_{t+1} = C_t \times (1 + \text{Insight Rate} + \text{Narrative Rate} - \text{Entropy Drain})$$

PantheonOS systematically reduces Entropy Drain via Praus, Sisyphus, Arctic, Bombadil, and Anthem Cadence. **This yields superlinear cognitive growth.**

